::Prowl/Kluster/Grimmler::

Prowl shakes his head at Iron Raptor's question. "No, there are two Predacon 
factions. Megatron still leads the second, I think. He'd probably use this 
chance to unite both."
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Kluster frowns at Iron Raptor's decition, looking at Battera. "I'll have one 
of my troops check your friend in," he says, tapping his comm-link.

"Grimmler," he says, "There's a Predacon near the base. He's here for 
peaceful reasons, and needs to be checked in."
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Recieving Kluster's orders, Grimler exits the Cybertronian Fire, looking at 
Cybershark.

"Are you the one here for 'peacefull purposes'?" he asks suspicioustly, his 
gun ready.
